title: The Complete Squirrel Girl Compilation
description:
This is a compilation of pretty much everything that has ever featured Squirrel Girl (Doreen Green.
It not only includes all of the comics but also has all of the animated appearances as well.

I previously did another torrent similar to this, but that was in no way complete. 

This is.

I have also written a list of all of the appearances of Squirrel Girl in Marvel media that is included in the files. Along with an assortment of random pictures i have found as well.

I hope you have fun reading and watching the adventures of Marvel's most powerful Super Hero!

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
